Documentation

This directory contains comprehensive documentation for the Smart Energy Monitoring System.

Contents

Images
 - Diagrams, screenshots, and photos of the system
Setup Guide
 - Step-by-step installation and configuration instructions
API Documentation
 - Details on the REST API and MQTT interfaces
User Manual
 - Instructions for end users
Quick Start

For a quick start guide, see the 
./setup_guide/README.md
.

API Reference

The system provides both REST API and MQTT interfaces for integration with other systems. See the 
./api/README.md
 for details.

Troubleshooting

Common issues and their solutions are documented in the 
./troubleshooting.md
